  "title": "남성역 한의원, 단순한 건망증이 아닐 수 있습니다 &ndash; 소양인이라면 더 주의하세요!",
  "addDate": "2025. 6. 23.",
  "categoryNo": "",
  "parentCategoryNo": "",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=metroparis&logNo=223908443647",
  "blocks": [],
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4349f8de-5cf8-4833-a578-b4db8e7da764\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-02d9c41b-ad6f-4ef9-8731-04eb97c6658d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f816075c-4269-4b78-b129-64b49bef8196\"><b>안녕하세요 남성역 한의원 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fce11d3f-40e3-4290-8037-a3ec1c6547b4\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3e68b721-b24e-4311-9789-5d3ec274dc19\"><b>이수한의원입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4349f8de-5cf8-4833-a578-b4db8e7da764\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-89fc6bdb-e020-432f-9a17-1383eea065d5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"1\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_1.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80a1f21a-e187-4134-bed7-9d2b01dbeda8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78138866-c7ce-4d0d-a241-d8046cc4b9d6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f59bbe89-0f32-4904-8c6f-f0c6d065cff7\">“내가 이걸 어디다 뒀더라?”, “무슨 말을 하려다 깜빡했지?”</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54cb71c9-8216-4934-abea-f4770baee504\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7563433b-b496-43de-99c9-3fc0862322eb\">일상 속에서 누구나 한 번쯤 겪는 건망증. 하지만 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-449a82fb-17ad-4843-b724-d864c7c22337\"><b>소양인에게는 이 건망증이 단순한 ‘깜빡함’이 아닐 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-80a1f21a-e187-4134-bed7-9d2b01dbeda8\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9a465711-38e6-4d73-bb40-89f969fc1a8a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-30428105-57a8-4fcf-9d6b-9f81c12a3b2e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-30428105-57a8-4fcf-9d6b-9f81c12a3b2e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/137cc74e3604ae01.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/137cc74e3604ae01.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/137cc74e3604ae01.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-30428105-57a8-4fcf-9d6b-9f81c12a3b2e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db3983b2-9590-43bc-bf8c-c6401e0d6325\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78f9a3d0-b26f-460f-9dfa-edfca47319f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3193fdb7-9899-483d-84f2-ce22766a41ca\"><b>✔ 소양인의 체질적 특성과 뇌기능</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-232f0dc3-cb14-47e2-b726-bd2a9ffae534\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5bff060c-e0b0-4f0a-ad66-abfce5e570de\">한의학에서는 사람의 체질을 크게 4가지(태양인, 소양인, 태음인, 소음인)로 나눕니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a51c56f-338d-4d28-9edf-7163c535ee31\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-18408e3e-1891-4ff4-a278-d1df01e9b428\">그 중</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e80ccf4b-3615-4aa3-9030-d61132c722f7\"><b> 소양인</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0ad1b143-396d-497e-87fb-f89820566acc\">은 ‘간이 강하고 신장이 약한 체질’로 분류되며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-328cd97e-eb5b-47c6-bca3-78010fffa05a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dcdf25e2-ec44-418e-bf9b-f19495ba51b2\"><b>열이 위쪽으로 몰리고 아래는 상대적으로 허약한</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3f3408c4-9876-421d-871c-dd559e6fc374\"> 특징을 지닙니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c1739a9-ae79-41bd-bd2e-28b4f871843b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-20077ee7-513b-4851-89f7-59d2e79a10a7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7cf486c9-5701-4225-b56f-38d94cfece4c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-517039d9-9b7e-4034-bc38-161584ea5640\">이러한 체질은 심리적, 정신적 긴장이나 피로가 누적되기 쉬우며, 그 결과 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f6002cf4-9830-48fa-9bdd-690e713f81b3\"><b>기억력 저하나 집중력 문제, 건망증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ecc234c8-e59f-4e75-9545-c4d290f5c1c2\">으로 나타날 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-db3983b2-9590-43bc-bf8c-c6401e0d6325\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-bc160ed0-7ed3-4b48-941a-687d5a1f841f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-479f4599-ed40-4bbf-a2a6-0cea8f066632\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b3ba50f-1075-4426-8eee-1c918ae1ac8d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f87428b5-9093-46fa-bea7-ddde12676e44\"><b>✔ 단순 건망증 vs 소양인의 위험 신호</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ebd3a49-6466-47f6-8de2-8e146231c969\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b53cf283-e046-47e5-88fc-711651cfef6c\">소양인의 건망증은 단순한 기억력 저하가 아니라, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cdff513e-ff92-4f34-bcd3-8d69a0dcb5a8\"><b>신체적 피로와 정신적 과로가 누적되면서 발생하는 뇌기능 이상</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-046c34f7-e601-4462-80cf-80e892c54ecd\">의 신호일 수 있습니다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-31772830-7e62-40e4-8df6-d001d68cad46\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d37818c6-7056-45b1-851c-a30caffb979b\">특히 다음과 같은 증상이 함께 있다면 주의가 필요합니다:</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6b60adce-293f-4114-99e4-71b076e25f23\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-25c68ee6-09ae-4d10-96f1-467efaa519fc\">일을 하다 자주 멍해지고 흐름을 놓침</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-df4e1e75-eb03-48e0-a8f3-66eba1ae8f63\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-eeae7e65-1f1c-47c1-b2c1-e8804310ec06\">대화를 하다 갑자기 무슨 말을 하려 했는지 잊어버림</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d343c73-beee-4e88-bc3f-1c32f54d4f98\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9ff3e4e7-3566-424a-8c76-939ae19f2a38\">평소보다 감정기복이 심해지고 예민해짐</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3326e268-f85e-471e-9939-2aadb20a7930\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2d9a76da-6575-4117-81b4-3f8061340592\">밤에 잠을 자도 개운하지 않음</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-479f4599-ed40-4bbf-a2a6-0cea8f066632\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b097f0f-f3e1-4da9-a4d7-830849714681\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:449px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9b097f0f-f3e1-4da9-a4d7-830849714681\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/677cbe45ae6e15a3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"970\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/677cbe45ae6e15a3.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/677cbe45ae6e15a3.png\" data-width=\"449\" data-height=\"425\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-9b097f0f-f3e1-4da9-a4d7-830849714681\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b800ff4-f2b8-4495-8a62-67efb2336382\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0baa216a-ac39-4c64-8da2-0c323ce1e8d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0b9c2e94-f751-4c67-8516-ea93b96c8ff4\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a3537bd-183b-440f-bbb6-034429d8e5ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-db002b6b-dd26-4c7e-94d0-77895b89e332\"><b>✔ 한의학적 치료 접근</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5bd48ee8-6db9-47cb-9da5-c524e1f99a83\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4c78d435-6d45-43c7-b677-1e6504c67e19\">소양인의 경우, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-19a1c756-17c2-4457-8760-f06bf64c71b1\"><b>두면(頭面)부로 열이 치솟고 하초는 냉한 경우</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0f9a4880-9a9c-41ca-84c5-351e4bbad076\">가 많아,</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-db6b8c5b-14ff-433d-b0ca-46e05ed4b1bd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-59462cda-8905-4c55-89b4-f5bed5dd40c7\">이러한 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c7db3ab2-78dc-4f38-b8dd-6d3afc7f8b2e\"><b>상열하한(上熱下寒)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4b889da4-f6c7-4c8f-8114-105f8d1033f3\"> 상태를 조절해주는 처방이 필요합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba7f8d3c-af0e-4635-8111-d40560d698c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-041893c9-92b8-43d4-859c-ae07919a13c9\">대표적으로는 아래와 같은 한약이 사용됩니다:</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83205a00-0c2e-4f32-8314-a38a43d1e970\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1c4ca189-d283-4a06-a397-5ad2f4b64e14\"><b>양격산화탕(凉膈散火湯)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-446edf03-d621-44e4-8cc9-8aa77229f323\">: 머리 쪽 열을 식히고 마음을 안정</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97db6d9b-dd8c-469d-beb5-b34ba73d853e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-06b89ed5-9e71-44e9-9e87-e437d01516a5\"><b>반하황련탕(半夏黃連湯)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-acaf526b-e408-4c5d-abc4-fd2d93086913\">: 위와 심장의 열을 내려 불안감·두근거림 완화</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a83b9eb-c027-4074-8d80-e36035544ca7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-69877a67-6edc-43e6-b8ba-8f8b03d94d2f\"><b>총명탕(聰明湯)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b1a98924-e34f-49fa-8307-5e2c91b85c17\">: 기혈을 맑게 하여 집중력·기억력 개선에 도움</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aea0b555-fbc3-4cfb-bb55-fa5495088822\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a052978d-bba8-4f81-b933-a146ee841f58\">또한, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-eac4803f-af72-4e02-8977-10f24dc98a67\"><b>침, 뜸, 약침요법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-051b6307-c325-4ebe-af65-75f3ecfea339\"> 등으로 뇌혈류를 원활하게 하고, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3cb18313-b245-4bc8-b46e-dabe03855eb6\"><b>신체 하부의 기능을 북돋는 보신요법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f692f9ad-532b-4fec-85e6-dd975314aba5\">을 병행하면 증상이 더 빠르게 개선될 수 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cae0ece7-160e-4185-b8d0-3e7a11ab5568\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-63bcf572-035b-4bed-913c-d735b86554e0\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e992c65f-32ff-4d81-a88b-3da210a820ae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-35328923-1a9d-4c66-b225-3b67612f9867\"><b>✔ 생활 속에서 실천할 수 있는 관리법</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24e180cf-84fc-4656-8013-935f88bbf849\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c80afb40-ffae-472a-9712-8fd2ba9e71fa\">카페인·자극적인 음식 줄이기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2698b0a-cd48-4e0f-8dc9-71693b5287c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a312e4a5-6fbd-4472-9c61-41069a161a76\">땀을 과도하게 흘리지 않도록 주의</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ab89c322-03e0-42cb-9c03-bcd1fd10ed01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-605ca1bb-7183-4c84-a492-afef90b81694\">충분한 수면과 명상, 스트레칭</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b0af7408-2e17-4340-a462-6c6193adf6d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b50fddf7-58a0-4cdd-8a3c-a67d0318ac0a\">두뇌 피로 해소를 위한 산책과 휴식</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23548a18-ff6b-4190-8da1-60d81eb9493b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7a25c310-9990-4921-9f42-aada7e9099d6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n   